premise_source_doc_sentence: Onika Tanya Maraj  (  born December 8 , 1982  )  , known professionally as Nicki Minaj  (  -LSB- langpronnɪkɪ_mɪ ` nɑːdʒ -RSB-  )  , is a Trinidadian-born American rapper , singer , songwriter and model .
`` The Boys '' is a song recorded by Trinidadian-American rapper Nicki Minaj and American singer Cassie .
